A subset of products ship from production. Cards are charged at order placement; orders may be cancelled any time before shipment. Browse: https://mytoywagon.com/collections/pre-order

## Shipping and policies

- Free shipping on orders $150+ within the contiguous 48 USA
- $9.95 flat rate under $150
- Limited international shipping to Canada, Mexico, China, France, Japan
- Returns within 30 days (return fee applies unless item is damaged)
- Shipping policy: https://mytoywagon.com/pages/shipping-policy

